@EventReservation.Server_HostAddress = https://localhost:7254

### Get event configuration (date, capacity, remaining seats)
GET {{EventReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/config
Accept: application/json

### Create a new reservation
POST {{EventReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phone": "+420 777 123 456",
  "ticketCount": 2
}

### Fetch a reservation by code (replace EVT-XXXXX with a real code)
GET {{EventReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/reservations/EVT-XXXXX
Accept: application/json

### Update a reservation
PUT {{EventReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/reservations/EVT-XXXXX
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "phone": "+420 777 123 456",
  "ticketCount": 4
}

### Cancel a reservation
DELETE {{EventReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/reservations/EVT-XXXXX

###
